, "channel": "foundconsciousness", "like_count": 5623, "comment_count": 140, "comments": [{"author": "witchworkshealingministry", "author_id": "31131509448", "id": "18099130646046318", "text": "YES Dr Richard Schulze taught me this terrific duo for any emergency back in 1994!!!! I barely even see lobelia mentioned! It's will give you the most hardcore purge ever!", "timestamp": 1775745252}, {"author": "barbmu68", "author_id": "1926157838", "id": "17930314611252513", "text": "I’ve been taking two capsules of cayenne pepper🌶️ (with food) for over 30 years. We have a history of circulation problems in the legs in my family. I’m the only one without issues and believe the cayenne pepper saved them.", "timestamp": 1775739285}, {"author": "aaisha1986", "author_id": "223217176", "id": "18008200127892623", "text": "Lobelia tincture and lobelia homeopathic remedy is still used today", "timestamp": 1775728204}, {"author": "equipmenttreenv", "author_id": "38305851586", "id": "17853308775644522", "text": "🔥", "timestamp": 1775725914}, {"author": "catch_n_snap_outdoors", "author_id": "5429869948", "id": "18084859499614806", "text": "🔥🔥", "timestamp": 1775701268}, {"author": "nyepennington", "author_id": "31344842668", "id": "18108330301680792", "text": "👏👏❤️", "timestamp": 1775663437}, {"author": "swalsh727", "author_id": "31234806850", "id": "18082586972371985", "text": "Thank You!🌻🌞", "timestamp": 1775653202}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/658316757_26149452001406565_2255361304926968567_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGtChPPUjkjxcLNy_nbqW_LA0G2z06eJVdiG2jij7z-p2KXl7EQsInPDfkQ-nVmdSU&_nc_ohc=xxYQnylJmjAQ7kNvwF7a9nG&_nc_gid=LBjY-kAWGHVfTadImzsK7A&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0z9m6ff_1NLQpDG5H9FV4Z-I599vniP3Z-RyLnp4aMSA&oe=69DE1FEA&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "hei